WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.680 --> 00:00:03.460
AND NOW A HIP-HOP NEWSBREAK

00:00:03.460 --> 00:00:05.000
WITH CHUCK TAYLOR

00:00:08.300 --> 00:00:09.940
GOOD EVENING,
I'M CHUCK TAYLOR.

00:00:09.975 --> 00:00:11.577
IT'S BEEN A VERY BUSY DAY
IN THE NEWS.

00:00:11.610 --> 00:00:13.112
A LOT OF THINGS HAVE HAPPENED.

00:00:13.145 --> 00:00:16.115
A STATEN ISLAND MAN IS LISTED
IN STABLE CONDITION TONIGHT

00:00:16.148 --> 00:00:18.551
AFTER A BRUTAL ASSAULT
BY RAPPER METHOD MAN

00:00:18.584 --> 00:00:20.019
FOLLOWING AN ARGUMENT.

00:00:20.052 --> 00:00:22.822
THE VICTIM ADDRESSED THE PRESS
EARLIER TODAY.

00:00:22.855 --> 00:00:27.193
IT WAS TORTURE.
STRAIGHT TORTURE, SON.

00:00:27.226 --> 00:00:29.662
FIRST HE PUT MY NUTS
ON THE DRESSER.

00:00:29.695 --> 00:00:31.697
IT WAS CRAZY--JUST MY NUTS.

00:00:31.730 --> 00:00:35.802
AND THEN HE BANGED THEM (BLEEP)
WITH A SPIKED BAT, LIKE "BOW!"

00:00:35.835 --> 00:00:37.136
[audience groans]

00:00:37.169 --> 00:00:40.106
AND THEN, HE SEWED
MY ASSHOLE SHUT.

00:00:40.139 --> 00:00:44.277
KEPT FEEDING ME
AND FEEDING ME AND FEEDING ME!

00:00:44.310 --> 00:00:46.879
THIS ALL TOOK PLACE IN
THE SLUMS OF SHAOLIN.

00:00:46.912 --> 00:00:49.615
THERE WAS THE RZA, THE GZA,
OL' DIRTY BASTARD,

00:00:49.648 --> 00:00:52.085
RAEKWON THE CHEF, U-GOD,
INSPECTAH DECK,

00:00:52.118 --> 00:00:55.054
AND OF COURSE, THE METHOD MAN.

00:00:55.087 --> 00:00:56.456
THE VICTIM ALSO SAID THAT

00:00:56.489 --> 00:00:58.024
AT ONE POINT
DURING THE ALTERCATION,

00:00:58.057 --> 00:00:59.692
METHOD MAN PUT A HANGER
ON THE STOVE

00:00:59.725 --> 00:01:01.727
AND LEFT IT
FOR, LIKE, 40 MINUTES

00:01:01.760 --> 00:01:04.330
AND THEN HE STUCK IT
IN HIS ASS REAL SLOW.

00:01:04.363 --> 00:01:07.333
LIKE, "SSS..."

00:01:07.366 --> 00:01:10.036
AT THIS POINT, METHOD MAN
IS STILL AT LARGE,

00:01:10.069 --> 00:01:13.739
SO STAY TUNED TO NEWS CHANNEL 3
FOR THIS AND OTHER STORIES.

00:01:13.772 --> 00:01:15.041
I'M CHUCK TAYLOR.

